  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK942">
<l>marunteṉa vēṇṭāvām yākkaik karuntiya</l>
<l>taṟṟatu pōṟṟi yuṇiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>No medicine is necessary for him who eats after assuring (himself) that what he has (already) eaten has been digested.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
